-the-80s-awesome-evolutions/4050-118846/">Decades: Marvel In The ''80s: Awesome Evolutions</a> (#21)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/marvel-weddings/4050-137619/">Marvel Weddings</a> (#21)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/amazing-spider-man-epic-collection-venom/4050-113053/">Amazing Spider-Man Epic Collection: Venom</a> (#22)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/amazing-spider-man-epic-collection-assassin-nation/4050-119132/">Amazing Spider-Man Epic Collection: Assassin Nation</a> (#23)</li><li><a href="/amazing-spiderman-epic-collection-round-robin/4050-80960/" data-ref-id="4050-80960">Amazing Spider-Man Epic Collection: Round Robin</a> (#25)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/spider-man-vibranium-vendetta/4050-126605/">Spider-Man: Vibranium Vendetta</a> (#25 (Main Story))</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/spider-man-the-new-warriors-the-hero-killers/4050-46628/" data-ref-id="4050-46628">Spider-Man &amp; the New Warriors: The Hero Killers</a> (#26)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/the-amazing-spider-man-brand-new-day-the-complete-/4000-648877/" data-ref-id="4000-648877">The Amazing Spider-Man: Brand New Day: The Complete Collection Vol. 4</a> (#36)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/spider-man-new-york-stories/4050-40487/">Spider-Man: New York Stories</a> (#37)</li><li><a href="/amazing-spider-man-the-gauntlet-the-complete-colle/4000-711939/" data-ref-id="4000-711939">Amazing Spider-Man: The Gauntlet: The Complete Collection Vol. 1</a> (#37)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/deadpool-classic-15-volume-15-all-the-rest/4000-516951/" data-ref-id="4000-516951">Deadpool Classic Volume 15</a> (#38)</li><li><a href="/deadpool-minibus-0-volume-0/4000-662086/" data-ref-id="4000-662086">Deadpool Minibus Volume 0</a> (#38)</li><li><a href="/the-amazing-spider-man-danger-zone/4050-58338/" data-ref-id="4050-58338">The Amazing Spider-Man: Danger Zone</a> (#39)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/avenging-spider-man-the-complete-collection/4050-118238/">Avenging Spider-Man: The Complete Collection</a> (#39)</li></ul><h4>Non-U.S. Collected Editions</h4><ul><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/visionarios-marvel-stan-lee/4050-95780/" data-ref-id="4050-95780">Visionarios Marvel: Stan Lee</a> (#1 &amp; #18) (Spanish)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/marvel-gold-doctor-extrano-1-maestro-de-las-artes-/4000-631690/">Marvel Gold. Doctor Extraño - Maestro de las Artes Místicas</a> (#2)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/80-jahre-marvel-3-die-1960er-aufbruch-in-eine-neue/4000-713394/">80 Jahre Marvel - Die 1960er: Aufbruch in eine neue Zeit </a>(#2-3) (German)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/maestros-marvel-john-romita-jr/4050-104383/" data-ref-id="4050-104383">Maestros Marvel. John Romita Jr.</a> (#11) (Spanish)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/coleccionable-marvel-heroes-6-spiderman-integral-f/4000-612211/" data-ref-id="4000-612211">Coleccionable Marvel Héroes - Spiderman: Integral Frank Miller </a>(#14-15) (Spanish)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/coleccionable-marvel-heroes-44-el-asombroso-spider/4000-612252/">Coleccionable Marvel Héroes - El asombroso Spiderman de Roger Stern y John Romita Jr.</a> (#16-17) (Spanish)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/coleccion-frank-miller-el-universo-marvel-segun-fr/4050-105405/">Colección Frank Miller. El Universo Marvel según Frank Miller</a> (#14-15) (Spanish)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/coleccionable-marvel-heroes-69-el-asombroso-spider/4000-612305/">Coleccionable Marvel Héroes - El asombroso Spiderman de Roger Stern y John Romita Jr. - Edición Definitiva</a> (#16-17) (Spanish)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/coleccionable-marvel-heroes-57-el-asombroso-spider/4000-612265/">Coleccionable Marvel Héroes - El Asombroso Spiderman: La era del traje negro</a> (#18-19) (Spanish)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/coleccionable-marvel-heroes-58-el-asombroso-spider/4000-612266/">Coleccionable Marvel Héroes - El Asombroso Spiderman: La identidad del Duende</a> (#21) (Spanish)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/spiderman-hulk-masacre-guerra-de-identidades/4050-103997/">Spiderman, Hulk &amp; Masacre: Guerra de identidades</a> (#38) (Spanish)</li></ul>', '1964', '33', 'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/0/4/6261-2189-6837-1-amazing-spider-man-a.jpg', '0');
INSERT INTO volumes (id, name, firstIssue, publisherId, deck, startYear, numIssues, image, numLikes) VALUES ('2190', 'Daredevil', 'The Origin of Daredevil', '31', '<p><em>He dwells in eternal night, but the blackness is filled with sounds and scents other men cannot perceive. Though attorney Matt Murdock is blind, his other senses function with superhuman sharpness; his radar sense guides him over every obstacle! He stalks the streets by night, a red-garbed foe of evil! Stan Lee presents... Daredevil, The Man Without Fear!</em></p><p>Unlike many <a href="/marvel/4010-31/" data-ref-id="4010-31">Marvel</a> heroes launched during the <a href="/silver-age-of-comics/4015-55821/" data-ref-id="4015-55821"> Silver Age of Comics</a>, Daredevil debuted in his own series without first being test launched in another title, as such, <em>Daredevil, The Man Without Fear</em> introduced readers to Matt Murdock in the first issue. The series started in 1964 and lasted 380 issues until being canceled in 1998. The title was selected to be part of the <a href="/marvel-knights/4015-58406/" data-ref-id="4015-58406">Marvel Knights</a> imprint and relaunched the series and character with <a href="/daredevil/4050-6209/" data-ref-id="4050-6209">Daredevil Vol. 2</a>.</p><h4>Additional Volumes</h4><ul><li>Daredevil Vol. 1</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/daredevil/4050-6209/" data-ref-id="4050-6209">Daredevil Vol. 2</a></li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/daredevil/4050-41410/" data-ref-id="4050-41410">Daredevil Vol. 3</a></li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/daredevil/4050-72417/" data-ref-id="4050-72417">Daredevil Vol. 4</a></li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/daredevil/4050-86343/" data-ref-id="4050-86343">Daredevil Vol. 5</a></li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/daredevil/4050-116964/" data-ref-id="4050-116964">Daredevil Vol. 6</a></li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/daredevil/4050-144027/" data-ref-id="4050-144027">Daredevil Vol. 7</a></li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/daredevil/4050-153465/" data-ref-id="4050-153465">Daredevil Vol. 8</a></li></ul><h4>Writers</h4><ul><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/stan-lee/4040-40467/" data-ref-id="4040-40467">Stan Lee </a>#1-9, 11-50 <strong>(TOT 49)</strong></li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/wally-wood/4040-6099/" data-ref-id="4040-6099">Wally Wood </a>#10</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/roy-thomas/4040-42067/" data-ref-id="4040-42067">Roy Thomas</a> #51-69, 71 <strong>(TOT 20)</strong></li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/gary-friedrich/4040-43812/" data-ref-id="4040-43812">Gary Friedrich</a> #70</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/gerry-conway/4040-40871/" data-ref-id="4040-40871">Gerry Conway</a> #72-98, 118 <strong>(TOT 27)</strong></li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/steve-gerber/4040-41456/" data-ref-id="4040-41456">Steve Gerber</a> #97-101, 103-117 <strong>(TOT 20)</strong></li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/chris-claremont/4040-40468/" data-ref-id="4040-40468">Chris Claremont</a> #102, 117, 375</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/tony-isabella/4040-42209/" data-ref-id="4040-42209">Tony Isabella</a> #119-123</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/marv-wolfman/4040-41478/" data-ref-id="4040-41478">Marv Wolfman</a> #124-139, 141-143 <strong>(TOT 19)</strong></li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/bill-mantlo/4040-42478/" data-ref-id="4040-42478">Bill Mantlo</a> #140</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/jim-shooter/4040-40450/" data-ref-id="4040-40450">Jim Shooter</a> #141, 144-151, 223 (TOT 10)</li><li><a href="/gil-kane/4040-1764/" data-ref-id="4040-1764">Gil Kane</a> #151</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/roger-mckenzie/4040-44822/" data-ref-id="4040-44822">Roger McKenzie</a> #151-161, 163-166, 183 <strong>(TOT 16)</strong></li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/michael-fleisher/4040-44657/" data-ref-id="4040-44657">Michael Fleisher</a> #162</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/david-michelinie/4040-40650/" data-ref-id="4040-40650">David Michelinie</a> #167</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/frank-miller/4040-7082/" data-ref-id="4040-7082">Frank Miller</a> #165-166, 168-191, 219, 226-233 <strong>(TOT 32)</strong></li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/alan-brennert/4040-42256/" data-ref-id="4040-42256">Alan Brennert</a> #192,</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/larry-hama/4040-12272/" data-ref-id="4040-12272">Larry Hama</a> #193</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/dennis-oneil/4040-40861/" data-ref-id="4040-40861">Dennis O''Neil</a> #18, 194-202, 204-207, 210-218, 220-223, 225, 226 <strong>(TOT 29)</strong></li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/steven-grant/4040-41567/" data-ref-id="4040-41567">Steven Grant </a>#203</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/harlan-ellison/4040-45706/" data-ref-id="4040-45706">Harlan Ellison</a>#208</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/arthur-byron-cover/4040-58547/" data-ref-id="4040-58547">Arthur Byron Cover</a> #208, 209</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/christopher-priest/4040-41500/" data-ref-id="4040-41500">Christopher Priest</a> #224</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/mark-gruenwald/4040-41607/" data-ref-id="4040-41607">Mark Gruenwald</a> #234</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/danny-fingeroth/4040-42531/" data-ref-id="4040-42531">Danny Fingeroth </a>#235</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/ann-nocenti/4040-42297/" data-ref-id="4040-42297">Anne Nocenti</a> #236, 238-245, 247-257, 259-291 <strong>(TOT 53)</strong></li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/steve-englehart/4040-42211/" data-ref-id="4040-42211">Steve Englehart</a> #237</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/jim-owsley/4040-103622/" data-ref-id="4040-103622">Jim Owsley</a> #246</li