 href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/avengers-west-coast-epic-collection-lost-in-space-/4050-121414/">Avengers West Coast Epic Collection: Lost In Space-Time</a> (#15)</li><li><a href="/avengers-the-contest/4050-34101/" data-ref-id="4050-34101">The Contest</a> (#16)</li><li><a href="/the-avengers-epic-collection-judgment-day/4050-75010/" data-ref-id="4050-75010">The Avengers Epic Collection: Judgment Day</a> (#16)</li><li><a href="/avengers-west-coast-avengers-zodiac-attack/4050-50388/" data-ref-id="4050-50388">Avengers: West Coast Avengers - Zodiac Attack</a> (#16)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/avengers-west-coast-epic-collection-tales-to-aston/4050-130576/">Avengers West Coast Epic Collection: Tales To Astonish</a> (#16)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/avengers-epic-collection-heavy-metal/4050-131882/">Avengers Epic Collection: Heavy Metal</a> (#17)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/avengers-by-john-byrne-omnibus/4050-92297/" data-ref-id="4050-92297">Avengers by John Byrne Omnibus</a> (#18)</li><li><a href="/avengers-epic-collection-the-collection-obsession/4050-109182/" data-ref-id="4050-109182">Avengers Epic Collection: The Collection Obsession</a> (#20)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/avengers-epic-collection-fear-the-reaper/4050-118237/">Avengers Epic Collection: Fear The Reaper</a> (#21)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/avengers-epic-collection-the-gatherers-strike/4050-123277/">Avengers Epic Collection: The Gatherers Strike!</a> (#22)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/avengers-the-gathering-omnibus/4050-134783/">Avengers: The Gathering Omnibus</a> (#22)</li></ul><h4>Non-U.S. Collected Editions</h4><ul><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/coleccionable-marvel-heroes-61-los-4-fantasticos-d/4000-612269/">Coleccionable Marvel Héroes - Los 4 Fantásticos de John Byrne 3</a> (#14) (Spanish)</li></ul>', '1967', '23', 'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/11/117763/2481750-avengersan01.jpg', '0');
INSERT INTO volumes (id, name, firstIssue, publisherId, deck, startYear, numIssues, image, numLikes) VALUES ('2351', 'Daredevil Annual', 'Electro and The Emissaries of Evil; Inside Daredevil; At the Stroke of Midnight!', '31', '<p>This series accompanies <a href="/daredevil/4050-2190/" data-ref-id="4050-2190">Daredevil vol. 1</a> and was released sporadically between 1967 and 1994. The stories are mainly one-off adventures that are unrelated to <a href="/daredevil/4005-24694/" data-ref-id="4005-24694">Daredevil''s</a> main story-lines. Issue 5 is mis-numbered as issue 4. In 1997 Daredevil teamed up with <a href="/deadpool/4005-7606/" data-ref-id="4005-7606">Deadpool</a> in <a href="/daredevildeadpool-annual-97/4050-26448/" data-ref-id="4050-26448">Daredevil / Deadpool ''97</a>. Since then the series has been published under two more #1s <a href="/daredevil-annual/4050-19415/" data-ref-id="4050-19415">Daredevil Annual</a> in 2007, and <a href="/daredevil-annual/4050-51109/" data-ref-id="4050-51109">Daredevil Annual</a> in 2012.</p><h4>Collected Editions</h4><ul><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/daredevil-omnibus-1-volume-1/4000-580744/" data-ref-id="4000-580744">Daredevil Omnibus Volume 1</a> (#1)</li><li><a href="/daredevil-epic-collection-mike-murdock-must-die/4050-108731/" data-ref-id="4050-108731">Daredevil Epic Collection: Mike Murdock Must Die!</a> (#1)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/daredevil-epic-collection-heart-of-darkness/4050-104463/" data-ref-id="4050-104463">Daredevil Epic Collection: Heart of Darkness</a> (#5-6)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/hulk-lifeform/4050-126604/">Hulk: Lifeform</a> (#6 (Main Story))</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/daredevil-epic-collection-last-rites/4050-132134/">Daredevil Epic Collection: Last Rites</a> (#7)</li><li><a href="/daredevil-epic-collection-fall-from-grace/4050-73013/" data-ref-id="4050-73013">Daredevil Epic Collection: Fall From Grace</a> (#10)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/black-widow-epic-collection-the-coldest-war/4050-130989/">Black Widow Epic Collection: The Coldest War</a> (#10)</li></ul><h4>Non-U.S. Collected Editions</h4><ul><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/visionarios-marvel-stan-lee/4050-95780/" data-ref-id="4050-95780">Visionarios Marvel: Stan Lee</a> (#1) (Spanish)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/coleccionable-marvel-heroes-55-daredevil-el-ocaso-/4000-612263/">Coleccionable Marvel Héroes - Daredevil: El ocaso de los ídolos</a> (#4) (Spanish)</li></ul>', '1967', '10', 'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/0/4/8707-2351-9614-1-daredevil-annual.jpg', '0');
INSERT INTO volumes (id, name, firstIssue, publisherId, deck, startYear, numIssues, image, numLikes) VALUES ('2353', 'Marvel Super-Heroes', 'The Coming of Captain Marvel', '31', '<p>Continues numbering from <a href="/fantasy-masterpieces/4050-2290/" data-ref-id="4050-2290">Fantasy Masterpieces </a>#11. It features original stories up to issue 20, after which it becomes a reprint series. The series is mostly known for the debut of <a href="/captain-marvel/4005-1472/" data-ref-id="4005-1472">Captain Mar-Vell</a> in issue 12. This led to <a href="/marvel/4010-31/" data-ref-id="4010-31">Marvel</a> attaining the rights to the "Captain Marvel" name and forcing <a href="/dc-comics/4010-10/" data-ref-id="4010-10">DC</a> to rename their Captain Marvel series to <a href="/shazam/4050-2622/" data-ref-id="4050-2622">Shazam!</a> Issue 13 of the series features the first appearance of <a href="//www.comicvine.com/ms-marvel/4005-21561/" data-ref-id="4005-21561">Carol Danvers</a>.</p><p>Issue 18 of the series features the first appearance of <a href="/guardians-of-the-galaxy/4060-25956/" data-ref-id="4060-25956">The Guardians of the Galaxy</a>.</p><h4>Collected Editions</h4><ul><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/marvels-captain-marvel-prelude/4050-116977/">Marvel''s Captain Marvel Prelude</a> (#13)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/captain-marvel-the-many-lives-of-carol-danvers/4050-129471/">Captain Marvel: The Many Lives of Carol Danvers</a> (#13)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/amazing-spider-man-epic-collection-the-goblin-live/4050-119744/">Amazing Spider-Man Epic Collection: The Goblin Lives</a> (#14)</li><li><a href="/amazing-spider-man-omnibus-4-volume-four/4000-883304/" data-ref-id="4000-883304">Amazing Spider-Man Omnibus Volume Four</a> (#14)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/inhumans-beware-the-inhumans/4050-107505/" data-ref-id="4050-107505">Inhumans: Beware the Inhumans</a> (#15)</li><li><a href="/marvel-masterworks-ka-zar-1-volume-1/4000-380710/" data-ref-id="4000-380710">Marvel Masterworks: Ka-Zar Volume 1</a> (#16)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/incredible-hulk-epic-collection-in-the-hands-of-hy/4050-121575/">Incredible Hulk Epic Collection: In the Hands of Hydra</a> (#16)</li><li><a href="/avengers-epic-collection-behold-the-vision/4050-81657/" data-ref-id="4050-81657">Avengers Epic Collection: Behold... The Vision</a> (#17)</li><li><a href="/avengers-omnibus-3-volume-three/4000-663568/" data-ref-id="4000-663568">Avengers Omnibus Volume 3</a> (#17)</li><li><a href="/guardians-of-the-galaxy-by-jim-valentino-3-volume-/4000-504337/" data-ref-id="4000-504337">Guardians of the Galaxy By Jim Valentino Volume 3</a> (#18)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/guardians-of-the-galaxy-by-jim-valentino-omnibus-1/4000-583938/" data-ref-id="4000-583938">Guardians of the Galaxy by Jim Valentino Omnibus Volume 1</a> (#18)</li><li><a href="/guardians-of-the-galaxy-earth-shall-overcome/4050-30359/" data-ref-id="4050-30359">Guardians of the Galaxy: Earth Shall Overcome</a> (#18)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/guardians-of-the-galaxy-tomorrows-heroes-omnibus/4050-116248/">Guardians of the Galaxy: Tomorrow''s Heroes Omnibus</a> (#18)</li></ul>', '1967', '94', 'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/11/117763/2481693-marvelsuper_heroes12.jpg', '0');
INSERT INTO volumes (id, name, firstIssue, publisherId, deck, startYear, numIssues, image, numLikes) VALUES ('2354', 'Not Brand Echh', 'The Silver Burper!; The Fastest Gums in the West!; The Human Scorch Versus the Sunk-Mariner!; A Day of Blunder!', '31', '<p>Marvel''s very first novelty comic-series. Some 6 years after the Marvel Age of Comics started in 1961, Marvel came up with the idea to make fun of their own characters. What came of it was this series, mostly hosted by <a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/forbush-man/4005-6808/">Forbush Man</a>. In 2018, a <a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/not-brand-echh/4050-106134/">Not Brand Echh</a> one-shot was published as number 14 of this series.</p><h4>Collected Editions</h4><ul><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/kingsize-kirby/4050-83141/">King-Size Kirby</a> (#1)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/marvel-masterworks-not-brand-echh/4050-82434/">Marvel Masterworks: Not Brand Echh</a></li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/not-brand-echh-the-complete-collection/4050-119863/">Not Brand Echh: The Complete Collection</a> (#1-13)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/captain-america-omnibus-1-volume-1/4000-274607/">Captain America Omnibus Volume 1</a> (#3)</li></ul><h4>Non-U.S. Collected Editions</h4><ul><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/kingsize-kirby/4050-104017/">King-Size Kirby</a> (#1) (Spanish)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/marvel-gold-capitan-america-3-el-quinto-durmiente/4000-631306/">Marvel Gold. Capitán América Volume 3: ¡El quinto durmiente!</a> (#3) (Spanish)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/visionarios-marvel-stan-lee/4050-95780/">Visionarios Marvel: Stan Lee</a> (#1-2 &amp; #7)</li></ul>', '1967', '13', 'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/0/4/8655-2354-9557-1-not-brand-echh.jpg', '0');
INSERT INTO volumes (id, name, firstIssue, publisherId, deck, startYear, numIssues, image, numLikes) VALUES ('2387', 'The Atom & Hawkman', '"Vengeance of the Silver Vulture"', '10', '<p>When sales of both Atom &amp; Hawkman were on the slide, the two comics combined, continuing number wise where the Atom left off. Running for 7 issues, the comic sometimes featured our heroes in a team up and at other times they were in separate adventures. Continues from <a href="/the-atom/4050-2051/" data-ref-id="4050-2051">The Atom</a></p><p>In 2010, DC resurrected the series for a single issue tied in to the Blackest Night event, #46.</p><h4>Collected Editions</h4><ul><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/blackest-night-10th-anniversary-omnibus/4050-119521/">Blackest Night 10th Anniversary Omnibus</a> (#46)</li></ul>', '1968', '8', 'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/0/9116/1106682-39.jpg', '0');
INSERT INTO volumes (id, name, firstIssue, publisherId, deck, startYear, numIssues, image, numLikes) VALUES ('2392', 'DC Special', 'An All-Infantino Issue', '10', '<p>Originally published between 1968 and 1971. Publication resumed in 1975 with <a href="/dc-special-16-super-heroes-battle-super-gorillas/4000-127310/" data-ref-id="4000-127310"><em>DC Special</em> #16</a>.</p>', '1968', '15', 'https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/0/3125/354289-2392-127307-1-dc-special.jpg', '0');
INSERT INTO volumes (id, name, firstIssue, publisherId, deck, startYear, numIssues, image, numLikes) VALUES ('2400', 'Captain America', 'This Monster Unmasked', '31', '<p>Captain America is on his own at last, in the comic that started it all, the Super Soldier''s story begins.</p><p>Continued from <a href="/tales-of-suspense/4050-2007/" data-ref-id="4050-2007">Tales of Suspense</a> issue 99. Tales of Suspense was one of several horror-like anthologies that Marvel was publishing in the early 1960''s, but just like its counterpart <a href="../../tales-to-astonish/49-2008/" rel="nofollow ">Tales To Astonish</a>, after nearly one hundred issues the series changed its name, after it already went a completely new route featuring characters such as <a href="/iron-man/4005-1455/" data-ref-id="4005-1455">Iron Man</a> and Captain America instead of horror stories. So it was that in 1968, the series became <a href="/captain-america/4050-2400/" data-ref-id="4050-2400">Captain America Volume 1</a> with its hundredth issue. Captain America ran on for three more decades much like its <a href="/the-incredible-hulk/4050-2406/" data-ref-id="4050-2406">Incredible Hulk</a> counterpart. The series concluded with issue 454, when the series was relaunched as <a href="/captain-america/4050-5776/" data-ref-id="4050-5776">Captain America vol. 2</a>. After issue number 50 of <a href="/captain-america/4050-11499/" data-ref-id="4050-11499">Captain America vol. 5</a>, that series returned to its original numbering started here in Volume 1, celebrating it''s 600th issue.</p><p>This is the first solo Captain America series published by <a href="/marvel/4010-31/" data-ref-id="4010-31">Marvel Comics</a>, the previous series, <a href="/captain-america-comics/4050-1628/" data-ref-id="4050-1628">Captain America Comics</a>, had been published by Marvel’s predecessors <a href="/atlas/4010-75/" data-ref-id="4010-75">Atlas</a> and <a href="/timely/4010-21/" data-ref-id="4010-21">Timely</a> respectively.</p><h4>Collected Editions</h4><ul><li><a href="https://www.comicvine.com/marvel-masterworks-captain-america-2-vol-2/4000-336526/" data-ref-id="4000-336526">Marvel Masterworks: Captain America Vol. 2</a> (#100)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/marvel-verse-captain-america/4050-129192/">Marvel-Verse: Captain America</a> (#100 &amp; 255)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/captain-america-omnibus-1-volume-1/4000-274607/" data-ref-id="4000-274607">Captain America Omnibus Volume 1</a> (#100-113)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/captain-america-epic-collection-the-coming-of-the-/4050-94262/" data-ref-id="4050-94262">Captain America Epic Collection: The Coming of... The Falcon</a> (#100-119)</li><li><a href="https://www.comicvine.com/marvel-masterworks-captain-america-3-vol-3/4000-233672/" data-ref-id="4000-233672">Marvel Masterworks: Captain America Vol. 3</a> (#101-113)</li><li><a href="https://www.comicvine.com/marvel-masterworks-captain-america-4-vol-4/4000-233673/" data-ref-id="4000-233673">Marvel Masterworks: Captain America Vol. 4</a> (#114-124)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/captain-america-omnibus-2-volume-2/4000-520197/" data-ref-id="4000-520197">Captain America Omnibus Volume 2</a> (#114-148)</li><li><a href="/marvels-captain-america-the-winter-soldier-prelude/4050-72369/" data-ref-id="4050-72369">Marvel''s Captain America: The Winter Soldier Prelude</a> (#117)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/captain-america-epic-collection-bucky-reborn/4050-102578/" data-ref-id="4050-102578">Captain America Epic Collection: Bucky Reborn</a> (#120-138)</li><li><a href="https://www.comicvine.com/marvel-masterworks-captain-america-5-vol-5/4000-233675/" data-ref-id="4000-233675">Marvel Masterworks: Captain America Vol. 5</a> (#125-136)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/modok-head-trips/4050-123130/">M.O.D.O.K.: Head Trips</a> (#133)</li><li><a href="https://www.comicvine.com/marvel-masterworks-captain-america-6-vol-6/4000-336470/" data-ref-id="4000-336470">Marvel Masterworks: Captain America Vol. 6</a> (#137-148)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/captain-america-epic-collection-hero-or-hoax/4050-112167/">Captain America Epic Collection: Hero Or Hoax?</a> (#139-159)</li><li><a href="https://www.comicvine.com/marvel-masterworks-captain-america-7-volume-7/4000-448248/" data-ref-id="4000-448248">Marvel Masterworks: Captain America Vol. 7</a> (#149-159)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/captain-america-the-legacy-of-captain-america/4050-40166/">Captain America: The Legacy of Captain America</a> (#155 &amp; 333)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/marvel-masterworks-captain-america-8-volume-8/4000-525028/" data-ref-id="4000-525028">Marvel Masterworks: Captain America Vol. 8</a> (#160-175)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/x-men-epic-collection-its-always-darkest-before-th/4050-120262/">X-Men Epic Collection: It''s Always Darkest Before the Dawn</a> (#172-175)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/marvel-masterworks-captain-america-9-volume-9/4000-591761/" data-ref-id="4000-591761">Marvel Masterworks: Captain America Vol. 9</a> (#176-192)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/captain-america-serpents-unite/4050-94263/" data-ref-id="4050-94263">Captain America: Serpents Unite!</a> (#163, 310, 313, 315)</li><li><a href="/captain-america-and-the-falcon-secret-empire-captain-america-and-the-falcon-secret-empire/4000-167746/" data-ref-id="4000-167746"> Secret Empire</a> (#169-176)</li><li><a href="/captain-america-the-75th-anniversary-vibranium-col/4050-87792/" data-ref-id="4050-87792">Captain America: The 75th Anniversary Vibranium Collection Slipcase</a> (#169-175, #255 and #445-448)</li><li><a href="/captain-america-and-the-falcon-nomad-captain-america-and-the-falcon-nomad/4000-167743/" data-ref-id="4000-167743"> Nomad</a> (#177-186)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/captain-america-evolutions-of-a-living-legend/4050-119523/">Captain America: Evolutions of a Living Legend</a> (#180, 337, 438 &amp; 451)</li><li><a href="/captain-america-peggy-carter-agent-of-shield/4050-78549/" data-ref-id="4050-78549">Captain America: Peggy Carter, Agent of S.H.I.E.L.D.</a> (#184-186)</li><li><a href="/captain-america-and-the-falcon-madbomb-captain-america-and-the-falcon-madbomb/4000-172445/" data-ref-id="4000-172445"> Madbomb</a> (#193-200)</li><li><a href="/marvel-masterworks-captain-america-10-volume-10/4000-676702/" data-ref-id="4000-676702">Marvel Masterworks: Captain America Vol. 10</a> (#193-200)</li><li><a href="/kingsize-kirby/4050-83141/" data-ref-id="4050-83141">King-Size Kirby</a> (#200)</li><li><a href="/captain-america-by-jack-kirby-bicentennial-battles-captain-america-by-jack-kirby-bicentennial-battles/4000-172446/" data-ref-id="4000-172446"> Bicentennial Battles</a> (#201-205)</li><li><a href="/marvel-masterworks-captain-america-11-volume-11/4000-713508/" data-ref-id="4000-713508">Marvel Masterworks: Captain America Vol. 11</a> (#201-214)</li><li><a href="/captain-america-and-the-falcon-the-swine-captain-america-and-the-falcon-the-swine/4000-167747/" data-ref-id="4000-167747"> The Swine</a> (#206-214, Annual #3, Annual #4)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/kirby-returns/4050-120559/">Kirby Returns!</a> (#208-212)</li><li><a href="/marvel-masterworks-captain-america-13-volume-13/4000-873645/" data-ref-id="4000-873645">Marvel Masterworks: Captain America Vol. 13</a> (#231-246)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/the-punisher-back-to-the-war-omnibus/4050-104072/" data-ref-id="4050-104072">The Punisher: Back To the War Omnibus</a> (#241)</li><li><a href="/captain-america-war-and-remembrance-captain-america-war-and-rememberance/4000-168483/" data-ref-id="4000-168483"> War and Remembrance</a> (#247-255)</li><li><a href="/captain-america-epic-collection-dawns-early-light/4050-71799/" data-ref-id="4050-71799">Captain America Epic Collection: Dawn''s Early Light</a> (#247-266)</li><li><a href="/marvel-universe-by-john-byrne-omnibus-1-hc/4000-523259/" data-ref-id="4000-523259">Marvel Universe by John Byrne Omnibus Volume 1</a> (#247-255)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/marvel-adventures-captain-america/4050-41523/">Marvel Adventures: Captain America</a> (#255)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/captain-america-epic-collection-monsters-and-men/4050-131207/">Captain America Epic Collection: Monsters and Men</a> (#267-285)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/defenders-epic-collection-the-sixfingered-hand-sag/4050-93423/" data-ref-id="4050-93423">Defenders Epic Collection: The Six-Fingered Hand Saga</a> (#268)</li><li><a href="/allnew-captain-america-fear-him/4050-82821/" data-ref-id="4050-82821">All-New Captain America: Fear Him</a> (#280)</li><li><a href="/deathlok-the-demolisher-the-complete-collection/4050-77316/" data-ref-id="4050-77316">Deathlok The Demolisher: The Complete Collection</a> (#286-288)</li><li><a href="/captain-america-death-of-the-red-skull/4050-47719/" data-ref-id="4050-47719">Captain America: Death of the Red Skull</a> (#290-301)</li><li><a href="/captain-america-epic-collection-society-of-serpent/4050-76582/" data-ref-id="4050-76582">Captain America Epic Collection: Society of Serpents</a> (#302-317)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/squadron-supreme-classic-omnibus/4050-90892/" data-ref-id="4050-90892">Squadron Supreme Classic Omnibus</a> (#314)</li><li><a href="/captain-america-scourge-of-the-underworld/4050-39209/" data-ref-id="4050-39209"> Scourge of the Underworld</a> (#318-320, #358-362)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/captain-america-epic-collection-justice-is-served/4050-100563/" data-ref-id="4050-100563">Captain America Epic Collection: Justice Is Served</a> (#318-332)</li><li><a href="/captain-america-the-captain/4050-40128/" data-ref-id="4050-40128"> The Captain</a> (#332-350)</li><li>