Men Milestones: Phalanx Covenant</a> (#305-306, 312-313 &amp; 316-317)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/x-men-the-wedding-of-cyclops-and-phoenix/4050-113273/">X-Men: The Wedding of Cyclops &amp; Phoenix</a> (#307-310)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/avengers-the-gathering-omnibus/4050-134783/">Avengers: The Gathering Omnibus</a> (#307)</li><li>Issues #308-310 are collected in <a href="/x-men-the-wedding-of-cyclops-and-phoenix-1-tpb/4000-361084/" data-ref-id="4000-361084">X-Men: The Wedding of Cyclops and Phoenix #1 - TPB</a></li><li>Issues #316-318 are collected in <a href="/origin-of-generation-x/4050-22011/" data-ref-id="4050-22011"> Generation X</a></li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/generation-x-epic-collection-back-to-school/4050-137802/">Generation X Epic Collection: Back To School</a> (#316-318)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/xmen-legion-quest/4050-109648/">X-Men: Legion Quest</a> (#318-321)</li><li>Issues #320-321 are collected in <a href="/x-men-legionquest/4050-35316/" data-ref-id="4050-35316"> Legionquest</a></li><li>Issues #322-326 are collected in <a href="/x-men-road-to-onslaught-1-volume-1/4000-443384/" data-ref-id="4000-443384">X-Men: Road To Onslaught #1 - Volume 1</a></li><li>Issues #327-328 are collected in <a href="/x-men-road-to-onslaught-2-volume-2/4000-457973/" data-ref-id="4000-457973">X-Men: Road To Onslaught #2 - Volume 2</a></li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/decades-marvel-in-the-90s-the-mutant-x-plosion/4050-119751/">Decades: Marvel In The ''90s: The Mutant X-plosion</a> (#328)</li><li>Issues #329-332 are collected in <a href="/x-men-road-to-onslaught-3-volume-3/4000-474809/" data-ref-id="4000-474809">X-Men: Road To Onslaught #3 - Volume 3</a></li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/x-men-prelude-to-onslaught/4050-37176/">X-Men: Prelude to Onslaught</a> (#333)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/x-men-milestones-onslaught/4050-124459/">X-Men Mil